description:
One today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to former Browns Offensive lineman Joe Thomas about Cleveland's decision to move on from Baker. Former Jets QB Mark Sanchez discusses Baker Mayfield's chances of landing in Seattle with his former coach Pete Carroll. And Sean Salisbury shares who he thinks will be the quarterback going forward in Houston.
